      <span class="mn">2</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> in absorbing medium with respect to the non-absorbing medium. Such study helps us estimate the necessary corrections/rectifications needed to the magnitudes of 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="M22" altimg="si5.svg" class="math">
    <div class="msub">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">n</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mn">2</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> and 
