   <div id="M23" altimg="si7.svg" class="math">
    <div class="msub">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">α</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mn">2</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> in absorbing medium and the corrections are linked with the ratios of linear AC and linear RI and that of imaginary and real parts of 
