   <div id="M24" altimg="si1.svg" class="math">
    <div class="msup">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">χ</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
      <span class="mn">3</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>. Quantitatively, it is done by computing the 
  <span class="italic">correction factor (CF)</span> for 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="M25" altimg="si5.svg" class="math">
    <div class="msub">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">n</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
